question: Question: An extremely endangered sparrowhawk and a similarly endangered scops owl are named for and found on Anjouan, an island in this archipelago.  [10] Identify this Indian ocean archipelago, the world's primary exporter of ylang-ylang. It currently contests ownership of the nearby islands of Mayotte with France.
